    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348120/extras/4ad290b1dda579ab89d86c4a03d5e812.poster.avif?t=1749282347\" width=616 height=215 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348120/extras/4ad290b1dda579ab89d86c4a03d5e812.webm?t=1749282347\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348120/extras/71afd6ee82518898798e35821b06edfb.avif?t=1749282347\" width=616 height=114 /></span>神乐宇宙出现了一些问题！一个神秘的存在正在试图撕裂时间与空间，使得各处的平行世界正在合而为一！解决眼下的危机，并恢复多元宇宙秩序的重任落在了女神的使者——神乐娘的肩上。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但事情远非神乐娘想象得那么简单……当她来到次元与次元间的通道时，她发现自己的能力居然消失了！每当她进入新的传送门之后，她的等级就会被重置为1级，变得和初出茅庐的冒险者无异。但即便如此，邪恶的势力也不会放缓追杀神乐娘的脚步……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在不同的次元间穿越，用手中的武器斩杀邪恶的怪物军团吧！只有这样，神乐娘才能让一切恢复正常，达成自己的使命！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348120/extras/a81f9516db90cc56ef545f2cb7603a15.poster.avif?t=1749282347\" width=616 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348120/extras/a81f9516db90cc56ef545f2cb7603a15.webm?t=1749282347\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348120/extras/1242fd71807e791a6bb02602ee89448d.avif?t=1749282347\" width=616 height=114 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348120/extras/bae417718efbdf9481db63640655ccb4.poster.avif?t=1749282347\" width=616 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348120/extras/bae417718efbdf9481db63640655ccb4.webm?t=1749282347\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348120/extras/22d2b98cc276cd1af30c2afe225f4ca1.avif?t=1749282347\" width=616 height=114 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348120/extras/73b90e361b41b85ebac7a7edb41be44c.avif?t=1749282347\" width=616 height=272 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348120/extras/e45596d107c3a3f05f8d9e70ef7cb391.avif?t=1749282347\" width=616 height=115 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348120/extras/52452216c42786121177faf8b309de56.avif?t=1749282347\" width=616 height=194 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348120/extras/a3a9f42b1671e53fa6826d26c5539e2f.avif?t=1749282347\" width=616 height=115 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348120/extras/c428fa451998ab269b86fdcd45e4e184.avif?t=1749282347\" width=616 height=419 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348120/extras/8